// Defences by type
// ----------------------------------------------------------------

Table: defences_Undead
Immunities: poison damage, the poisoned condition. Resistances: necrotic, [|cold|lightning|bludgeoning from non-magical weapons].
Immunities: poison, exhaustion, the poisoned condition. Resistances: necrotic, cold.
Immunities: poison damage. Resistances: necrotic damage; bludgeoning, piercing, slashing from non-magical attacks.

Table: defences_Beast
Resistances: none. Vulnerabilities: [|fire|thunder|lightning]. Immunities: the frightened condition.
Resistances: [|bludgeoning|piercing|slashing] from non-magical weapons. Immunities: none.
Resistances: none. Senses reveal this creature detects predators at unusual range.

Table: defences_Humanoid
Resistances: none. Saving throw proficiencies: [|STR + CON|DEX + INT|WIS + CHA].
Resistances: [|fire (from armour)|poison (veteran constitution)|bludgeoning (thick hide)]. Immunities: none.
Resistances: none. Immunities: the frightened condition (battle-hardened).

Table: defences_Fiend
Immunities: fire, poison damage; the poisoned condition. Resistances: cold, lightning, bludgeoning/piercing/slashing from non-magical non-silver weapons.
Immunities: fire damage. Resistances: cold, lightning, poison; non-magical weapon damage.
Immunities: fire, poison. Resistances: cold, lightning; bludgeoning, piercing, slashing from non-magical weapons.

Table: defences_Dragon
Immunities: [|fire|cold|lightning|poison|acid] damage. Resistances: [|bludgeoning|piercing|slashing] from non-magical weapons.
Immunities: [|fire and poison|cold and exhaustion|acid and the poisoned condition]. Saving throw proficiencies: DEX, CON, WIS, CHA.
Immunities: [|fire|cold|lightning|acid|poison] damage. Resistances: none listed separately — scales provide exceptional natural armour.

Table: defences_Construct
Immunities: poison, psychic; the poisoned, exhausted, frightened, charmed, paralysed conditions.
Immunities: poison, psychic damage; poison and disease conditions. Resistances: non-magical bludgeoning, piercing, slashing.
Immunities: poison, psychic; exhaustion, fear, charm, paralysis, disease, poison condition.

Table: defences_Aberration
Immunities: psychic damage (some). Resistances: [|cold|fire|acid|lightning]. Saving throw proficiencies: INT, WIS.
Resistances: psychic damage. Immunities: the charmed and frightened conditions.
Immunities: none common. Resistances: psychic; bludgeoning, piercing, slashing from non-magical weapons.

Table: defences_Fey
Immunities: the charmed condition. Resistances: [|fire|cold|necrotic|bludgeoning from non-magical weapons].
Immunities: none. Resistances: [|radiant|fire|poison] damage; charm effects have disadvantage.
Immunities: poison damage; the poisoned and charmed conditions. Resistances: bludgeoning, piercing, slashing from cold-iron weapons.

Table: defences_Giant
Resistances: none common. Saving throw proficiencies: STR, CON.
Resistances: [|cold|fire|lightning] damage. Immunities: the frightened condition.
Resistances: bludgeoning, piercing, slashing from non-magical weapons (thick hide). No immunities.

Table: defences_Ooze
Immunities: [|acid|lightning|cold|fire] damage; the blinded, deafened, exhausted, prone conditions.
Immunities: acid damage; blinded, deafened, prone, exhaustion. Resistances: [|fire|cold].
Immunities: acid, [|cold|fire]. Conditions immune: blinded, deafened, exhausted, frightened, prone.

Table: defences_Plant
Immunities: poison, psychic; the blinded, deafened, poisoned conditions. Resistances: [|fire|cold|necrotic].
Vulnerabilities: fire damage. Resistances: piercing damage. Immunities: psychic; blinded, deafened.
Immunities: psychic; the blinded and deafened conditions. Resistances: [|cold|bludgeoning|necrotic].

Table: defences_Monstrosity
Resistances: [|bludgeoning from non-magical weapons|poison|fire]. Immunities: [|the petrified condition|the charmed condition].
Immunities: [|fire|acid|poison] damage. Resistances: [|cold|lightning|bludgeoning from non-magical weapons].
Saving throw proficiencies: STR, CON. Resistances: [|bludgeoning|piercing] from non-magical weapons.

