Spore Burst (Recharge 5–6): 20 ft radius cloud of spores; CON save (DC {1d4 + 12}); on failure, target is poisoned for 1 minute and {1d4} turns later falls unconscious (another CON save to resist).
Thorn Volley: Ranged attack, range 30/120 ft; +{1d4 + 4} to hit; Hit: {2d6 + 3} piercing damage.
Root Snare: One creature within 20 ft makes DEX save (DC {1d4 + 13}) or is restrained by roots; STR save (DC {1d4 + 13}) to break free.
Regrowth: Regains {2d8 + 4} HP and sheds any conditions affecting it (costs its action; can be used once per short rest).
Blight Aura (Recharge 5–6): All plant life within 30 ft withers; the area becomes difficult terrain for 1 hour. Non-plant creatures in the area take {2d6} necrotic damage.

