Bite: Melee attack +{1d4 + 5} to hit, reach 5 ft. Hit: {2d10 + 4} piercing damage.
Claw: Melee attack +{1d4 + 5} to hit, reach 10 ft. Hit: {2d6 + 4} slashing damage.
Sting (Recharge 5–6): Melee attack +{1d4 + 5} to hit. Hit: {2d8 + 4} piercing damage plus {2d8} poison damage; CON save (DC {1d4 + 13}) or paralyzed for 1 minute.
Gore: Melee attack +{1d4 + 6} to hit, reach 5 ft. Hit: {2d8 + 5} piercing damage; target makes STR save (DC {1d4 + 14}) or is knocked prone.
Trample: Moves through one creature's space; creature makes DEX save (DC {1d4 + 13}) or takes {4d8 + 5} bludgeoning damage and falls prone.
Swallow: Melee attack vs grappled creature; on hit, creature is swallowed (blinded, restrained, {2d6} acid damage per turn).
Petrifying Gaze (Recharge 5–6): One creature in line of sight makes CON save (DC {1d4 + 13}) or is restrained; another failed save at start of its next turn petrifies it.
Tail Sting: Melee attack +{1d4 + 5} to hit, reach 15 ft. Hit: {2d6 + 4} piercing damage + {2d8} poison damage.

